data.description: PRICE REDUCED! MOTIVATED SELLER! Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Cypress Mill Community! This immaculate 2020 home is ready for you now! Situated on a beautifully landscaped lot, this stunning two-story residence boasts four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. The heart of this home is the fully equipped kitchen, complete with upgraded stainless steel appliances, ample granite counter space, plenty of cabinets, and a spacious pantry for all your storage needs. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the large living and dining rooms, making it perfect for entertaining. There's even a convenient half bathroom on the first floor. Upstairs, you'll discover the spacious master suite with a private bathroom and a generously sized walk-in closet. Additionally, there are three other well-appointed bedrooms and a versatile loft, ideal for family game nights or a home office. The second-floor laundry room adds a touch of convenience for the entire family. This home is a true gem, barely lived in, and in pristine condition, thanks to the previous owner's frequent travels. Cypress Mill residents enjoy an array of resort-style amenities, including a community clubhouse, sport courts for basketball and tennis, a shaded play area, a dog park, and a luxurious pool. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Schedule your viewing today because this remarkable property will not last long. Your dream home awaits!
